Interface TemplateProvider.GeneratedTemplateProvider

All Superinterfaces:

Enclosing interface:
TemplateProvider
public static interface TemplateProvider.GeneratedTemplateProvider extends TemplateProvider, JStachioTemplateFinder.SimpleTemplateFinder
Generated template providers implement this interface to support easier ServiceLoader registration for modular libraries/applications. It is mainly an implementation detail and not recommended for manual usage.
